# Remote Sync Architecture

Job registry and tracker store both live on huh.desktop.us as the single source of truth.

## Job Registry

fuyao_job_manager.py auto-pushes the registry to huh.desktop.us:~/software/Experiment-Tracker-/fuyao_job_registry.json on every write via _save_registry(). No manual sync needed.

## Tracker Store

Tracker recordings run directly on huh.desktop.us via record_tracker_remote.sh. The script scp's the payload and executes the tracker CLI on the remote. No local-to-remote sync needed.
